# Starter content manifest for local MaccabiPedia dev wiki.
#
# One page title per line. Lines starting with '#' and blank lines are
# ignored. Titles must be spelled exactly as on the wiki (including Hebrew
# characters, spaces, colons for namespaces, etc.).
#
# Special:Export auto-includes every template referenced by these pages,
# so you get realistic infobox/Cargo rendering even from a small manifest.
#
# Edit freely — expand coverage as you need it. After changing, re-run:
#   ./scripts/sync-from-prod.sh pages scripts/content-manifests/starter.manifest
#   ./scripts/seed-content.sh starter

# --- core ---
עמוד ראשי

