# Add titles below exactly as they appear on maccabipedia.co.il (URL-decoded).
# Extend with games, seasons, coaches, stadiums, prose articles, and category
# pages as you need realistic content to test against.
ערן זהבי
שרן ייני
אצטדיון בלומפילד
